3
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:50,679
Sirs,

4
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,079
you...

5
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:59,904
(Ye Dong, new CEO of Jiuyao Group
is a Live-in Son-in-Law)

6
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:09,280
Mr. Cheng,

7
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:11,180
Mr. Ye Dong is asking to see you.

8
00:01:14,180 --> 00:01:16,299
(He has been so moody lately.)

9
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:17,640
(That look in his eyes)

10
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:18,719
(scared me to death.)

11
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:21,379
Should

12
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:22,459
I send him in?

13
00:01:24,540 --> 00:01:25,980
Show Mr. Ye in.

14
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:27,379
Right away.

15
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:44,859
Hello.

16
00:01:44,859 --> 00:01:46,099
Mr. Cheng will see you now.

17
00:01:49,459 --> 00:01:50,260
Wait here.

18
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:06,099
Have a seat.

19
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,500
Ye Dong,

20
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:10,379
what brings you here?

21
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:12,340
What a wonderful surprise!

22
00:02:14,539 --> 00:02:15,900
When I passed by earlier,

23
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:17,500
the sign read Cheng Nuo.

24
00:02:17,819 --> 00:02:18,780
My gut told me

25
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:19,699
it is you,

26
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:20,939
so I dropped in.

27
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:22,699
You...

28
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:23,500
I must admit,

29
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,379
your gut is sharp.

30
00:02:26,939 --> 00:02:28,099
I just saw the news

31
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:29,060
that

32
