you're taking over Jiuyao Group.

33
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:34,020
Who would've thought?

34
00:02:34,340 --> 00:02:36,699
You're the Lin family's son-in-law!

35
00:02:37,580 --> 00:02:38,979
Your good fortune

36
