219
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,600
truly claim your destiny.

220
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:27,039
Once he achieves his goal,

221
00:12:29,279 --> 00:12:30,679
I'll send your daughter

222
00:12:30,679 --> 00:12:31,919
